            <p>08/16/2024 - I went to Hanauma Bay on my Birthday. The waters were crystal-clear and there was plenty of marine life. I saw a triggerfish as I was snorkeling!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card" data-location="Byodo-In Temple, Hawaii">
            <a href="I2.jpg"><img src="I2.jpg" alt="Byodo-In Temple, Hawaii"></a>
            <p>08/16/2024 - The Byodo-In Temple was a peaceful experience with its lush greenry and breathtaking architecture. Inside the temple, there was a Buddha statue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card" data-location="Lanikai Beach, Hawaii">
            <a href="I3.jpg"><img src="I3.jpg" alt="Lanikai Beach, Hawaii"></a>
            <p>08/18/2024 - Lanikai Beach was the most relaxing beach and had the softest white sands. Went kayaking to a smaller island nearby called The Mokuluas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card" data-location="Manoa Falls, Hawaii">
            <a href="I4.jpg"><img src="I4.jpg" alt="Manoa Falls, Hawaii"></a>
            <p>08/19/2024 - Manoa Falls is a must-visit hiking destination with a stunning waterfall surrounded by lush rainforest scenery. Even though it was pouring rain, it was such a surreal moment with nature.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card" data-location="Sunset Beach, Hawaii">
            <a href="I5.jpg"><img src="I5.jpg" alt="Sunset Beach, Hawaii"></a>
            <p>08/23/2024 - This photo was taken on the last day of my trip to Hawaii. Sunset Beach is known for its sunsets and it didn't dissapoint!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-card" data-location="Shark Cove, Hawaii">
            <a href="I6.jpg"><img src="I6.jpg" alt="Shark Cove, Hawaii"></a>
            <p>08/21/2024 - Shark's Cove offered plenty of marine life to see as you snorkel. I saw the fish Gill from Finding Nemo. Highly reccomend!</p>
